{"tid":548681,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【時代在變】日本澡堂「裸體授課」 諗計吸年輕人幫襯救亡","createTime":"2018-02-02T21:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T01:19:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e24e707e5d612addb9f5c80bab09f565ae0eae1","tid":548681,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T21:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496065913_2d43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496065913_2d43.jpg&h=b7c79251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時國際  2017-05-31 01:04:02 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n東京一間傳統公共澡堂為了吸引年青人光顧，竟然想出變身為「裸體學校」，邀請「教師」在澡堂內裸體授課。<br />\n<br />\n9名男子圍坐在澡堂內，聽著一名專家講述圍棋精要，其中一名聽課者表示，「如果年青人知道這裡提供這些課程，會有興趣光顧公共澡堂。」<br />\n<br />\n澡堂經理田村裕一（音譯）稱，他們的澡堂是家族生意，自1939年便開始經營，他指出澡堂全盛時期，每天有逾500人光顧，但現時已減至大約100人。他指出現時很多年青人都因家中有浴室，故從未光顧公共澡堂，「我想透過提供一些特別活動如裸體學校，給他們一個光顧的理由。」"},{"pid":"c9dca70a0c9d4ad48b1e31c5f4cb6eb1213f2c2a","tid":548681,"uid":56505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T21:34:07.000Z","msg":"引hehe?"},{"pid":"87ebae588b3f730e33d3f590259dacea98c4ae3c","tid":548681,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T21:48:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02ed27ea51a2cd33659c938d2c8c8a9d48fc3acc","tid":548681,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ebae588b3f730e33d3f590259dacea98c4ae3c","tid":548681,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T21:48:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T22:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78eafd78e2705de1c323f7f0fb4122bc089ff4ff","tid":548681,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T23:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 